Package ClientSide.controllers

'controllers' package contains the classes which has the UI logic.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdministratorController
    AdministratorController : Managed the Administrator UI.
    BaseController
    BaseController: an abstract base class which handling with not desirable disconnection from server and controlling the GUI initialization process.
    CompanyEmployeeController
    CompanyEmployeeController : Managed the Company Employee UI.
    Costumer_SavedData
    Costumer_SavedData: Class that manages the data of the costumer when creating reservation.
    CostumerController
    CostumerController: Manage the costumer UI functionalities.
    CostumerServiceEmployeeController
    CostumerServiceEmployeeController: Manages the costumer service employee UI.
    LoginController
    LoginController: Create first connection with the server and login to the system, the controller related to 'Login.FXML' and 'LoginSettings.FXML' .
    LoginSettingsController
    LoginController: Create first connection with the server and login to the system.
    ServiceSpecialistController
    ServiceSpecialistController: manages the service specialist UI.
    ShopEmployeeController
    ShopEmployeeController: Manages shop employee UI.
    ShopManagerController
    ShopManagerController : Managed the Shop Manager and Chain Manager UI.
    UserDetailsController
    UserDetailsController: Controller that related to UserDetails.fxml

Package ClientSide.controllers Description

'controllers' package contains the classes which has the UI logic.

'Client' project contains all the functionality of the client side.
